## Error Handling

| Error | Solution |
|-------|----------|
| WebSearch rate limit | Wait and retry (1x), then proceed with partial results |
| No results found | Broaden query terms, try English + Japanese |
| Agent timeout | Continue with partial results from completed agents |

## Troubleshooting

### Few results returned
- Generalize the search terms
- Try both English and Japanese queries
- Search for broader category instead of specific topic
